<strong>Optional mod integrations</strong>

<strong>Rune-Story</strong> (if loaded)
Runic pickaxes become craftable at high tier. The runic pickaxe qualifies as runite-tier for dragon mining.

<strong>Primitive Survival</strong> (if loaded)
The <a href="metals">metal ladder</a> extends into PS content:
• Mithril / adamantite / runite / dragon fishing hooks.
• Mithril / adamantite / runite / dragon fishing lures.
• Mithril / adamantite / runite / dragon spike-plate traps.

<strong>Lang patches</strong>
Included for PS items so display names read correctly when the integration loads.
